buildCommand:
mkdir -p docs && cp ../docs/*.md docs/ && echo '---
layout: page
title: Changelog
description: Release history and version notes for GNO
permalink: /changelog/
---
' > changelog.md && cat ../CHANGELOG.md >> changelog.md && bundle exec jekyll build
devCommand:
mkdir -p docs && cp ../docs/*.md docs/ && echo '---
layout: page
title: Changelog
description: Release history and version notes for GNO
permalink: /changelog/
---
' > changelog.md && cat ../CHANGELOG.md >> changelog.md && bundle exec jekyll serve --livereload
